ario analyses: 1) expansion of forest, 2) expansion of agricultural land. The two land-use scenarios are generated using proximity-based approaches where the user determines which land-use type can be converted to, as well as the type of patterns based on proximity of the edge of focal land use. Results of the scenario analysis demonstrate the potential changes of carbon stocking to land cover and land-use change. © 2022 IEEE.
