TI  - Research On Multimorbidity In Primary Care. Selected Abstracts From The Egprn Meeting In Tampere, Finland, 9-12 May 2019 All Abstracts Of The Conference Can Be Found At The Egprn Website: Www.egprn.org/Page/Conference-Abstracts
