e of perioperative narcotics for patients. Conclusions and Relevance: This review notes actionable, evidence-based practices to reduce medical overuse in dermatology. This work may help to facilitate management changes to emphasize high-value care in dermatology while promoting awareness and further evaluation of overuse in medicine. © 2019 American Medical Association. All rights reserved.
