s in vegetation cover were observed in Xichuan and Neixiang counties while environmental degradation is evident in the broader Danjiang River watershed. Key factors influencing these spatial variations include elevation and soil composition in addition to climate variables such as rainfall and temperature. Infrastructure projects like the South-to-North Water Diversion Project and targeted ecological conservation policies have also positively impacted vegetation within the basin. © 2023 The Author(s)
