vironment impact is a promising direction for the development of integrated environmental and economic assessment of the results of nature management at the regional level. Comparison of the carbon intensity with the carbon sequestration potential could be used to improve the structure of land use for environmental management purposes. © 2021 Moskovskij Universitet. All rights reserved.
