erminals as the main channel of communication or as a contingency solution. During the last 5 years the solution has been installed in more than 1500 points around Latin America, including Brazil in their main electric companies with excellent results of improvement of SAIDI and SAIFI, allowing these companies to manage the devices deployed in the field and making strategic decisions in real time. © 2019 IEEE.
